-- Investigation Into LVMH's Hermes Stake May Take a Year, Regulator Says
-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 2010-11-10T06:51:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/investigation-into-lvmh-s-hermes-stake-may-take-a-year-regulator-says.html
An investigation by France’s
financial regulator into LVMH Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton SA’s
stake in Hermes International SCA may take a year, AMF head
Jean-Pierre Jouyet said in an interview on Canal Plus television
station.  France’s law on takeovers needs to be clearer, Jouyet said
in the interview.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  